="nymphs-index.htm">Nymphs</a></font></td></tr><tr><td valign="top" height="46"><p align="center"><font face="Arial" color="#383838">Picture & Symbols of Polyhymnia</font></td></tr></table><div align="center"><div align="center"><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="98%" height="30"><tr><td width="37%" valign="top"><p align="center">&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr></table><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="99%" height="120"><tr><td><p align="center"><script async src="//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js"></script>
